  The Pretty Woman actor looked positively smitten with his wife as they gazed into each other’s eyes in one of the photographs. Alejandra, who is a publicist, is over 30 years her husband’s junior and the couple share two sons. A-lister Richard looked dapper as he posed for the camera in a smart black suit and dark blue shirt. Meanwhile, Alejandra turned up the glamour in a deep red gown with a pleated skirt and some sparkly silver jewellery.  